        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0633P0_20020325_GCR_79' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        7 p.m.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0633P0-00604'>
        <a name='S5LV0633P0_20020325_GCR_80'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-william-mccarthy' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
